<br>
Sega's in a sad state now.  The Dreamcast was a pretty cool system, and it's amazing how spectacularly the company failed.  To be gobbled up by MS or EA... /shudder.  If I had to choose, I'd rather see EA buy Sega, since MS would certainly slave them to the X-Box.<br>
<br>
